# New York Pizza Dough

> Source:
> - https://www.sipandfeast.com/homemade-pizza-dough-new-york-pizza/#wprm-recipe-container-7590

## Ingredients

> Makes four 15-inch pizzas

- 813g bread flour
- 521g water @40C
- 16g salt 
- 27g olive oil
- 9.5g sugar
- 3g instant dry yeast

- Cornmeal or semolina for dusting the peel

